            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Common marketing applications include: monitoring brand mentions on social media, analyzing customer reviews at scale, routing negative support tickets to priority queues, measuring campaign reception, and tracking competitor perception.</p></div></div>
          </div>
